data.description: Attention Buyers!!!  Recently renovated 3BR/2BA  home in good neighborhood.  Neighborhood is close to Lisenby Elementary and Carroll High School.  Dale County Lake and Stegall Park are within walking distance.  Inside has been repainted.  Hardwood floors, doors and new fixtures are newly installed.  Small porch and large deck are great for family gatherings. Home includes a large den, bonus room, fireplace and new stainless steel appliances.  This is a must see for home buyers!!
data.whatILove: Beautiful remodel. Floors are all wood look vinyl. Neutral gray wall paint throughout. Nice stainless appliances and back splash. large "man cave" or den downstairs with beautiful brick fireplace. All decks/porches are new. GREAT neighborhood within walking distance or lake, park, walking trail, fishing, archery park, basketball & tennis courts. Lisenby Elementary and Carroll High are all within walking distance. LARGE master with sitting area and nice size walk in closet
